Standard Operating Procedure: How to Purchase an Item on Jumia

Step 1: Create or Log Into Your Account
Open the Jumia app
If you do not have an account, select “Sign Up”
Enter your phone number, email, and password
If you already have an account, select “Log In” and enter your details

Step 2: Browse or Search for a Product
From the home page, scroll to view available products
To browse by category, select “Categories”
To search for a specific item, select the search bar
Type the product name and select from the results

Step 3: Select Product
Tap on the desired product
Review product details
Select quantity using the plus (+) button

Step 4: Add Item to Cart
Select “Add to Cart”
Confirm the item has been added in the correct quantity

Step 5: Proceed to Checkout
Select the “Cart” icon
Review items in your cart
Select “Checkout”

Step 6: Choose Payment Method
Select one of the following options:
Pay with bank card
Pay with M-Pesa
Pay with Airtel Money
Lipa Pole Pole
Pay on delivery
Complete payment as instructed

Step 7: Confirm Order
Review order details
Confirm purchase
Wait for order confirmation

Step 8: Track Order
Go to “Account”
Select “Orders”
View order status and updates

