TROUBLESHOOTING TIPS
This answers, What users should do when something goes wrong
Examples….
Problem:
Search gives no results.
Solution:
Try product keywords instead of descriptions.
Problem:
Wrong item delivered.
Solution:
Open account → orders → request return.
Problem:
Payment fails.
Solution:
Check network, balance, then retry.

